CatDescriptText: Cutline of article published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 12, 1963, pg. 8 reads: "Green Links Entertain at Smart Fete - A gay and exciting mood was experienced by those attending the pre-New Year's Masked Ball given by the smart Green Link Golf Club, Dec. 30, at the exclusive Green Oaks Country Club."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of two men wearing suits, and two women, one wearing dress with sheer sleeves, posed as couples around coffee table in Green Oaks Country Club during Green Link Golf Club's Masked Ball
